      "rationale": "Experimental test conditions documented with calibrated flow loop instrumentation. Flow rates measured with Coriolis meter (±0.5% accuracy); rotational speed with optical encoder (±0.1%). Temperature controlled at 37±0.5°C. All five operating points replicated three times; repeatability confirmed with CV < 3%."
