      "rationale": "CFD-predicted hemolysis index compared against experimental measurements using normalized index of agreement (d = 0.94) and mean absolute percentage error (MAPE = 4.2%). All predictions fall within combined experimental and numerical uncertainty bands. Worst-case operating condition correctly identified by model in agreement with experimental rank ordering."
