      "rationale": "Validation activities conducted on FDA generic centrifugal blood pump geometry under physiologically representative conditions (flow rates 2–6 L/min, rotational speeds 2500–4500 RPM, blood analog fluid with matched viscosity). Validation domain overlaps with COU operating envelope; extrapolation outside validated range is not required for the five specified operating points."
    },
    {
