      "rationale": "At MRL 2, rigorous model form uncertainty quantification is not required. The SST k-omega turbulence model with curvature correction is an established choice for rotating machinery hemolysis prediction per FDA benchmark studies. Model form selection is justified by literature precedent and confirmed adequate by the output comparison results."
